Package registry.element

Class DataElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • registry.element.DataElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AStrLDataElement, AStrZDataElement, BinDataElement, IntDataElement, LongDataElement, ShortDataElement, UStrLDataElement, UStrZDataElement
    public abstract class DataElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines an element of specified type at specified offset into RegistryBuffer This is the base (abstract) class Concrete element types will descend from here
